import React from 'react'
import Tasbeeh from './Projects/TasbeehCounter/Tasbeeh'
import {Routes, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Nav from './Projects/Nav'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Nav/>
      <Routes>
        <Route path={"/score"} element={<ScoredScore />}/>
      </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
